line_1: Next, Dick, if Chance her self shou'd vary;
By Arts improve the Stuffs they vary;
line_2: And Things are best, as most contrary.

line_1: Howe'er swift Alma's Flight may vary;
Each does her studious Action vary,
line_2: To go and come, to fetch and carry:
With learned Skill, now push, now parry,

line_1: You laugh, if Coat and Breeches strangely vary,
line_2: White Gloves, and Linnen worthy Lady Mary!
